# Proxy Supabase through our own domain so the browser never needs to talk to supabase.co.
# Anything hitting /auth/, /rest/, /storage/, /functions/, /realtime/ on this site
# gets transparently forwarded to the real Supabase project.
#
# Result: no DNS blocks, no ad-blocker lists, no CORS headaches. Works on every network
# like any other normal app.

/auth/*       https://thjotelpvxonkvkycsga.supabase.co/auth/:splat       200!
/rest/*       https://thjotelpvxonkvkycsga.supabase.co/rest/:splat       200!
/storage/*    https://thjotelpvxonkvkycsga.supabase.co/storage/:splat    200!
/functions/*  https://thjotelpvxonkvkycsga.supabase.co/functions/:splat  200!
/realtime/*   https://thjotelpvxonkvkycsga.supabase.co/realtime/:splat   200!
